Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:41.27,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌聲中搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:50.88,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:02:01.64,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}閉上雙眼 看到的
